description: These cat emoticons look like they belong in an anime. Something about Φs for eyes makes me think of the Azumanga Diaoh cat. Can you see it? It adds so much character that these cats are truly memorable. A lot of these kitty emotes don’t even have whiskers, but their eyes and mouths let us know they are supposed to be cats.
